channel.title: My first time using peoples scripts?
channel.description:
hi basically i'm very new to scar and when i try to use peoples scripts i really dont know what to do at all?!?!? do i click run? do i click compile? do i have to set colors? all those i dont understand and when i click run or compile they all come up with a very similar error message like this
"Failed when compiling Line 161: [Error] (20150:1): Unknown identifier 'SetScreenName' in script C:\DOCUME~1\Kevin\LOCALS~1\Temp\EYCutterBankerV104-1.scar"
by the way i have SRL and it is up to date. please help me i want to auto for runescape. pleeeease!!
